---
title: SuperQuick Indian-Inspired Curried Turkey Bowls with Golden Rice Pilaf and Creamy Tomatoes
description: Treat yourself to a dish featuring aromatic flavours inspired by Indian samosas. Veggie-studded rice pilaf and cooling raita-style cucumbers ensure a wholesome meal the whole family will love.

